msgctxt "Languages::rus_taxes.upgrade_message.tax_conversion"
msgid "<p>— Starting with January 1, 2019, [product] will offer you to automatically change all tax rates from 18% to 20%. You'll only need to confirm it (that requires signing in to the admin panel). You can also update the rates manually — learn more <a href=\"https://forum.cs-cart.ru/t/cs-cart-i-izmeneniya-v-zakonodatelstve-1-yanvarya-2019-g/6816\">at our Russian forum</a>.</p>"
msgstr "<p>— Starting with January 1, 2019, [product] will offer you to automatically change all tax rates from 18% to 20%. You'll only need to confirm it (that requires signing in to the admin panel). You can also update the rates manually — learn more <a href=\"https://forum.cs-cart.ru/t/cs-cart-i-izmeneniya-v-zakonodatelstve-1-yanvarya-2019-g/6816\">at our Russian forum</a>.</p>"
